CardanoSummit2021EtM0014.name: Cardano Summit 2021: Enter the Metaverse [0014]
description: Step right up kids,
We know It's been one wild and bumpy ride
Getting jostled from one empire to the next
Everyone slept through most of it
If I'm being honest!
Don't worry, the alarm clock just started going off -
So it must be time
A blue symbol so sublime, off in the distance
Here's the remote, so let's gather round
I think it'll be best if we all go through together
Just remember, keep that eye open and don't doze off
It can be easy to let the moon distract you
It's real nifty, but its still not what it's all about
Especially when the Sun'll cast greater light throughout
The azure is filling up - Is it? Could it be?
It's a cascading disruption in the pattern!
Auspicious and bright sounds erupt as everyone takes off
their VR glasses
A celebration
Happy Summit, everyone!
